Changi Exhibition Centre, the third Covid-19 community isolation facility, received its first patients on Saturday (April 25). The repurposed space houses recovering patients, or newly confirmed cases with mild symptoms. 
The facility is the first to use robots and teleconsultation in patient care. 
Video: Raj Nadarajan/TODAY
